	<li>Cap on Amount of Charitable Donation Deduction: $111,000 ($108,000 in =
2024)&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Worldwide gross revenue limit for Qualified Family-Owned Small Busines=
s deduction: $11,095,000&nbsp;($10,790,000 in 2024)</li>
</ul>
</div>

